div.font: With the increasing complexity of the problems ahead, it would require breakthroughs at each of the levels of computer stack while keeping in mind their interoperability with other layers. Hence, I find it challenging as an aspiring computer architect to explore the cross-stack optimizations for future applications. Therefore, I would be interested in working with a diverse group of students (either in a single group or through collaborations) who have expertise at different levels of system hierarchy and can work together towards a common problem.
